== Romanian ==
===Adjective===
'''olog'''
#A person or thing missing a foot or leg or both feet or legs.
#A person or thing who doesn't walk well; a person or thing who limps or walks slowly or awkwardly.
#A person or thing whose legs are paralyzed or unusable.
=== Etymology ===
Unknown. Has an Albanian [[cognate]].


